org.gephi.ui.tools.plugin.edit

Class EditNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      • org.openide.nodes.Node
        • org.openide.nodes.AbstractNode
          • org.gephi.ui.tools.plugin.edit.EditNodes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openide.util.HelpCtx.Provider, org.openide.util.Lookup.Provider

    public class EditNodes
extends org.openide.nodes.AbstractNode
    PropertySheet that allows to edit one or more nodes. If multiple node edition mode is used at first all values will be shown as blank but will change with the editions and all nodes will be set the values that the user inputs.
    Author:
    Mathieu Bastian
